name: Jagruti Foundation
briefDescription: Jagruti Foundation is Located in Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra.We are working on 1. Chid health & care.2.Women Empowerment.3.Anti Tobacco awareness programme we got Narotam Seksaria award in 2014 By the hands of WHO heath director.We are working for poor including dalit & minorities.With the support of Navi Mumbai municipal Corporation we organise Street plays to create awareness of Swatch bharat Abhiyan.
